{"trainType":"强基计划","grade":"2021","education":{"id":2,"nameZh":"本科"},"studentType":{"id":4,"nameZh":"普通"},"department":{"id":89,"code":"206","nameZh":"化学与材料科学学院"},"major":{"id":1,"code":"20601","nameZh":"化学"},"majorDirection":null,"requiredCredits":160,"awardDegree":true,"beginSemester":"2021年秋季学期","directionGen":true,"moduleTree":[{"self":{"id":35723,"parent":35722,"type":"通修课程","typeEn":"General Courses","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":8,"requiredCourseNum":2,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[{"compulsory":true,"weeks":null,"totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":null,"course":{"id":142140,"code":"PHYS1001A","nameZh":"力学A","nameEn":"Mechanics A","totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"credits":4,"introduction":"<p>力学是大学第一门普通物理课程，主要介绍与描述、研究物体机械运动有关的基本概念、基本理论和相关研究方法，包括质点运动学、牛顿动力学等，以及建立在此基础上关于振动与波、刚体、流体等的基本理论；除此之外，还简单介绍狭义相对论的基本内容。</p>","courseGradation":"通修","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["1秋"],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（半开卷）","department":{"id":87,"code":"203","nameZh":"物理学院"}},{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":5,"course":{"id":10056,"code":"PHYS1004A","nameZh":"电磁学A","nameEn":"Electromagnetism A","totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"credits":4,"introduction":"<p>电磁学A是一门关于电磁现象及电磁相互作用的课程，是自然科学重要基础课之一。内容涉及在真空、导体、介质中的静态和随时间演变的电场和磁场规律，主要章节包括电场、磁场、电磁力、导体与介质的电磁特性、电磁感应、直流电和交流电、麦克斯韦电磁方程组和电磁波。通过本课程学习，能深刻认识电磁现象的基本规律，掌握电磁相互作用的基本理论和应用，培养严密的科学思维能力，熟练掌握数学工具在电磁学中的应用， 以及了解电磁学在现代科学技术发展中的作用。</p>","courseGradation":"通修","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["1春"],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（闭卷）","department":{"id":87,"code":"203","nameZh":"物理学院"}}],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":0},"isLeaf":true}]}